{"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview\/setselected:animated:"]}],"sections":[],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"metadata":{"title":"setSelected:animated:","role":"symbol","symbolKind":"method","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"- "},{"text":"setSelected:animated:","kind":"identifier"}],"externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNAnnotationView(im)setSelected:animated:","roleHeading":"Instance Method","remoteSource":{"fileName":"MLNAnnotationView.h","url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNAnnotationView.h#L230"},"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"text","text":"- "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setSelected:animated:"}]},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView"]]},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView\/setSelected:animated:"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Sets the selection state of the annotation view with an optional animation."}],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS","iPadOS","Mac Catalyst"],"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"kind":"text","text":"- ("},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:v","text":"void","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"setSelected:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"BOOL","preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@BOOL"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"selected"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"animated:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@BOOL","text":"BOOL","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"animated","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"parameters":[{"name":"selected","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"code":"YES","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" if the view should display itself as selected; "},{"code":"NO","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"if it should display itself as unselected."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"name":"animated","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"code":"YES","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" if the change in selection state is animated; "},{"code":"NO","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" if the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"change is immediate."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"kind":"parameters"},{"mentions":["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre-Native-for-iOS\/AnnotationViewExample"],"kind":"mentions"},{"content":[{"text":"Discussion","level":2,"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"You should not call this method directly. A map view calls this method in","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"response to user interactions with the annotation. Subclasses may override this","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"method in order to customize the appearance of the view depending on its","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"selection state.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Related examples","level":4,"anchor":"Related-examples","type":"heading"},{"items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre-Native-for-iOS\/AnnotationViewExample"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"type":"unorderedList"}],"kind":"content"}],"kind":"symbol","references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotationView/setSelected:animated:":{"fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"setSelected:animated:","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"setSelected:animated:","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Sets the selection state of the annotation view with an optional animation."}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview\/setselected:animated:","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView\/setSelected:animated:","role":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotationView":{"fragments":[{"text":"MLNAnnotationView","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"MLNAnnotationView","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView"},{"type":"text","text":" class is responsible for marking a point annotation"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"with a view. Annotation views represent an annotation object, which is an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"object that corresponds to the "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation"},{"type":"text","text":" protocol. When an annotation’s"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"geographic coordinate is visible in the map view, the map view asks its"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"delegate to a corresponding annotation view. If an annotation view is created"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"with a reuse identifier, the map view may recycle the view when it goes"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"offscreen."}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView","role":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"role":"collection","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling."}],"type":"topic","title":"MapLibre","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre-Native-for-iOS/AnnotationViewExample":{"title":"Custom Annotation View","role":"article","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre-Native-for-iOS\/AnnotationViewExample","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre-native-for-ios\/annotationviewexample","abstract":[{"text":"Add a custom annotation view","type":"text"}],"kind":"article"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotation":{"fragments":[{"text":"MLNAnnotation","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"MLNAnnotation","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation"},{"type":"text","text":" protocol is used to provide annotation-related information"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to a map view. To use this protocol, you adopt it in any custom objects that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"store or represent annotation data. Each object then serves as the source of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"information about a single map annotation and provides critical information,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"such as the annotation’s location on the map. Annotation objects do not provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the visual representation of the annotation but typically coordinate (in"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"conjunction with the map view’s delegate) the creation of an appropriate"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"objects to handle the display."}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","role":"symbol"}}}